{"tid":553194,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2/11]一團火DSE 應試分享會2018（第２場）- 2月11日約定您","createTime":"2018-02-07T08:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T04:05:15.000Z","uid":114788,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a37d5ef09d40437ffe757c20134c8fbe699356","tid":553194,"uid":114788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠100日就ＤＳＥ啦! 2018dser 你地準備成點？ <br />\n<br />\n一團火義補計劃會喺11/2係城大舉行DSE分享會，由幾位喺DSE攞到佳績嘅過來人分享中、英、數、通識科的應試心得，為各位打打氣，誠邀各位應屆ＤＳＥ考生參加。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅同學可以透過下面條link係google form報名，費用全免㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">莫問前程凶吉　但求落幕無悔<br />\n共勉之！</span></span></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iny0Fc54Ft0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIny0Fc54Ft0&d=y%2Bec4sQHKQqngYfow8DPRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=085bed5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iny0Fc54Ft0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/233905_a1ba27b7775c774d2ae83b210fd0cd29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F233905_a1ba27b7775c774d2ae83b210fd0cd29.jpg&h=55c20bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【一團火】DSE應試分享會 - 報名表（中學生）: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/j5CKp5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fj5CKp5&d=y%2Bec4sQHKQqngYfow8DPRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f7f441f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/j5CKp5</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n                  DSE應試分享會詳情<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n日期：2018年2月11日（星期日）<br />\n時間：10:30-11:25 通識科<br />\n            11:30-12:30 中文科<br />\n            13:30-14:30 英文科<br />\n            14:35-15:30 數學科<br />\n地點：香港城市大學<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------